cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and summarization. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses neural networks for summarization. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as summarization is a common task in this field. The paper also involves domain adaptation, which is a common topic in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
